<!--================ Enlisted ================-->

<!--======== Trooper & Gunner ========-->

	<BackstoryDef ParentName="CFAR_Reichswehr">
		<defName>CFAR_RW_Infantry1</defName>
		<title>Reichswehr infantry</title>
		<titleShort>trooper</titleShort>
		<description>When [PAWN_nameDef] was still a kitten, [PAWN_possessive] always looked up to soldiers—they carried themselves with an effortless confidence. After joining the Reichswehr, [PAWN_nameDef] quickly learned the art of “keep calm and bullshit through,” discovering that confidence could be practiced as much as it was worn.</description>
		<requiredWorkTags>
			<li>Social</li>
		</requiredWorkTags>
		<skillGains>
			<Shooting>6</Shooting>
			<Melee>2</Melee>
			<Social>4</Social>
		</skillGains>
		<spawnCategories>
			<li>CFAR_RW_Infantry</li>
		</spawnCategories>
	</BackstoryDef>

	<BackstoryDef ParentName="CFAR_Reichswehr">
		<defName>CFAR_RW_Infantry2</defName>
		<title>Reichswehr infantry</title>
		<titleShort>trooper</titleShort>
		<description>When [PAWN_nameDef] joined the Reichswehr, [PAWN_pronoun] had high hopes of fighting the enemies of the Kaiserin, shoulder to shoulder with capable, confident comrades. To be fair, that part turned out to be true. What no one mentioned was the endless trench digging and encampment work—most of it done with a shovel.</description>
		<requiredWorkTags>
			<li>Constructing</li>
			<li>Mining</li>
		</requiredWorkTags>
		<skillGains>
			<Shooting>7</Shooting>
			<Melee>3</Melee>
			<Construction>2</Construction>
			<Mining>2</Mining>
		</skillGains>
		<spawnCategories>
			<li>CFAR_RW_Infantry</li>
		</spawnCategories>
	</BackstoryDef>

	<BackstoryDef ParentName="CFAR_Reichswehr">
		<defName>CFAR_RW_Infantry3</defName>
		<title>Reichswehr infantry</title>
		<titleShort>trooper</titleShort>
		<description>In hindsight, [PAWN_nameDef] should have thought twice before applying for infantry. [PAWN_pronoun] had severely underestimated the sworn enemy of all infantry—marches. Now everything ached, and [PAWN_nameDef] had only [PAWN_objective]self to blame while bandaging blistered feet.</description>
		<requiredWorkTags>
			<li>Caring</li>
		</requiredWorkTags>
		<skillGains>
			<Shooting>6</Shooting>
			<Melee>4</Melee>
			<Medicine>2</Medicine>
		</skillGains>
		<spawnCategories>
			<li>CFAR_RW_Infantry</li>
		</spawnCategories>
	</BackstoryDef>

